    "content_toggles_xUDexC": {
      "type": "content-toggles",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ViJhqr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "1. What makes Ganguram Sweets one of the best sweet shops in Kolkata?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Ganguram Sweets is widely regarded as one of the best sweet shops in Kolkata, known for its authentic Bengali sweets, premium ingredients, and heritage dating back to 1885. Popular items include Rosogolla, Jalbhara Sandesh, Mishti Doi, and Kaju Katli.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_tGFxWf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "2. Does Ganguram Sweets offer sweets for festivals and special occasions?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, Ganguram Sweets offers a wide range of festival sweets and premium gift boxes ideal for occasions like Diwali, Durga Puja, weddings, corporate gifting, and celebrations. Customised gift hampers are also available.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_EVxLhj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. Are the sweets at Ganguram Sweets prepared fresh daily?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, all sweets at Ganguram Sweets are prepared fresh daily using high-quality milk, khoya, dry fruits, and traditional recipes to ensure authentic taste and superior quality.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_BRLUXP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "4. Why is Ganguram Sweets considered the best sweet shop in Kolkata?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Ganguram Sweets is known for its legacy, authentic Bengali recipes, hygienic preparation, consistent taste, and customer trust built over more than a century. Its innovation in sweets and premium packaging also sets it apart.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_ragMPm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "5. Does Ganguram Sweets provide online sweets delivery?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, Ganguram Sweets offers online delivery across Kolkata and PAN India. Customers can easily order sweets, gift boxes, and hampers through the official website.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_nHQTjT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "6. What are the most popular sweets at Ganguram Sweets?",
            "subtitle": "Question subtitle",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Some of the best-selling sweets include:</p><ul><li>Jalbhara Sandesh</li><li>Rosogolla (Tin & Fresh)</li><li>Mishti Doi</li><li>Kaju Katli</li><li>Khirer Chop</li></ul>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_T3BdmV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "7. Does Ganguram Sweets offer gift packaging?",
            "subtitle": "Question subtitle",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Yes, premium gift boxes and customised packaging options are available, making them ideal for gifting during festivals, weddings, and corporate events.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        },
        "text_DeA3XL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "8. Where are Ganguram Sweets stores located?",
            "subtitle": "Question subtitle",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Ganguram Sweets has multiple outlets across Kolkata, along with online delivery services for customers across India. Our flagship stores are located at <strong>Beadon Street, Alambazar, Ariadaha, and Misti Hub (Eco Park)</strong>.</p>",
            "hide_block_if": false
          }
        }
      },
